Offbeat Broadway 5 — Behaving Badly: Directed by comedian Alan Committie and starring Anton Luitingh, Paul du Toit and Lindy Abromowitz, this send-up brings together some of the most loved and loathed musicals in a 70-minute irreverent romp. Details: The broadway show will take place until June 2 at The Drama Factory, 25 Comprop Square, Henry Vos Close, Asla Business Park, Strand.
